ww.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片131.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-431\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片131.jpg\" alt=\"图片13\" width=\"686\" height=\"457\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片141.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-432\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片141.jpg\" alt=\"图片14\" width=\"686\" height=\"457\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片151.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-433\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片151.jpg\" alt=\"图片15\" width=\"684\" height=\"456\" /></a>\r\n\r\n“执子之手，与子偕老。”这就是我对你的承诺。\r\n\r\n新郎轻轻掀起头纱，新娘的笑容融化所有人的心。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片171.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-435\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片171.jpg\" alt=\"图片17\" width=\"685\" height=\"456\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片181.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-436\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片181.jpg\" alt=\"图片18\" width=\"685\" height=\"456\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片191.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-437\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片191.jpg\" alt=\"图片19\" width=\"685\" height=\"457\" /></a>\r\n\r\nLove is like a butterfly. It goes where it pleases and it pleases where it goes. 我的爱与你同在。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片20.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-439\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片20.jpg\" alt=\"图片20\" width=\"836\" height=\"557\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片211.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-440\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片211.jpg\" alt=\"图片21\" width=\"829\" height=\"553\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片221.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-441\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片221.jpg\" alt=\"图片22\" width=\"832\" height=\"555\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片23.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-442\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片23.jpg\" alt=\"图片23\" width=\"811\" height=\"541\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片24.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-443\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片24.jpg\" alt=\"图片24\" width=\"811\" height=\"541\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片25.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-444\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片25.jpg\" alt=\"图片25\" width=\"803\" height=\"535\" /></a>\r\n\r\nDREAMER通过精心布置和安排，只为新人的婚礼能尽善尽美。2014年7月19日，DREAMER为你掀开人生的新篇章-------情绵绵，爱无边！\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片26.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-446\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片26.jpg\" alt=\"图片26\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片27.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-447\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片27.jpg\" alt=\"图片27\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片28.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-448\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片28.jpg\" alt=\"图片28\" width=\"897\" height=\"598\" /></a>','2014.07.19巴厘岛乌布蝴蝶森林婚礼实录','','inherit','open','open','','414-revision-v1','','','2014-09-29 12:49:51','2014-09-29 04:49:51','',414,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/?p=449',0,'revision','',0),(450,1,'2014-09-29 13:04:30','2014-09-29 05:04:30','“无际的蓝色大海，轻轻地泛起白色的浪花，温婉，单纯，就像是你我之间的耳语。”---我定会如白玫瑰花语般，爱护你，珍惜你。\r\n\r\nDREAMER8.09，新人选择的场地是：宝格丽水上婚礼。平静的水面中，倒映着的，是宝格丽纯净的蓝；绚丽的阳光下，墙上倒映着的，是斑驳的树影；而新人眼中倒映的，是彼此的笑颜。DREAMER希望给您的，不仅是一场唯美奢华的婚礼，而是能够令两位拥有永远紧紧相依的决心。\r\n\r\n08.09这一天，最不舍的便是母亲了。20多年的养育之恩，最好的回报就是看着儿子成家立室，幸福地步入人生的另一个阶段。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片29.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-451\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片29.jpg\" alt=\"图片29\" width=\"2794\" height=\"1863\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片30.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-452\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片30.jpg\" alt=\"图片30\" width=\"2794\" height=\"1863\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片311.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-453\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片311.jpg\" alt=\"图片31\" width=\"2794\" height=\"1863\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"p0\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">兄弟们戴上鸡蛋花一起前去接新娘，做新郎背后最铁的支援！</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\"><a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片321.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-454\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片321.jpg\" alt=\"图片32\" width=\"2880\" height=\"1920\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片33.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-455\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片33.jpg\" alt=\"图片33\" width=\"2880\" height=\"1920\" /></a></p>\r\n一条铺满粉红色花瓣的喜道，漂浮在剔透的无边泳池上，为宝格丽纯净的蓝，增添了许多甜蜜的气氛。如此的海天一色，怎么有人不SAY YES?感谢DREAMER团队的用心布置！\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片38.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-456\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片38.jpg\" alt=\"图片38\" width=\"3264\" height=\"2448\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片34.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-457\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片34.jpg\" alt=\"图片34\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2880\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片35.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-458\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片35.jpg\" alt=\"图片35\" width=\"2880\" height=\"1920\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片36.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-459\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片36.jpg\" alt=\"图片36\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2880\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片37.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-460\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片37.jpg\" alt=\"图片37\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2880\" /></a>\r\n\r\n从今以后，两家人变一家人，你=我。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片39.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-461\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片39.jpg\" alt=\"图片39\" width=\"2880\" height=\"1920\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"p0\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">L</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">ove is a vine that grows into our hearts.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">爱是长在我们心里的藤蔓。</span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">D</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">reamer<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">希望你们能够</span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">—</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">深情每一刻，深爱每一天。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\"><a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片40.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-462\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片40.jpg\" alt=\"图片40\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2880\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片411.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-463\" src=\"http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片411.jpg\" alt=\"图片41\" width=\"1397\" height=\"932\" /></a></p>','宝格丽水上婚礼','','publish','open','open','','%e5%ae%9d%e6%a0%bc%e4%b8%bd%e6%b0%b4%e4%b8%8a%e5%a9%9a%e7%a4%bc','','','2014-09-29 15:13:02','2014-09-29 07:13:02','',0,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/?p=450',0,'post','',0),(451,1,'2014-09-29 12:56:37','2014-09-29 04:56:37','','图片29','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8729','','','2014-09-29 12:56:37','2014-09-29 04:56:37','',450,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片29.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(452,1,'2014-09-29 12:56:45','2014-09-29 04:56:45','','图片30','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8730','','','2014-09-29 12:56:45','2014-09-29 04:56:45','',450,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片30.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(453,1,'2014-09-29 12:56:50','2014-09-29 04:56:50','','图片31','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8731','','','2014-09-29 12:56:50','2014-09-29 04:56:50','',450,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片311.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(454,1,'2014-09-29 12:57:33','2014-09-29 04:57:33','','图片32','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8732','','','2014-09-29 12:57:33','2014-09-29 04:57:33','',450,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片321.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(455,1,'2014-09-29 12:57:42','2014-09-29 04:57:42','','图片33','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8733','','','2014-09-29 12:57:42','2014-09-29 04:57:42','',450,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片33.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(456,1,'2014-09-29 12:59:47','2014-09-29 04:59:47','','图片38','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8738','','','2014-09-29 12:59:47','2014-09-29 04:59:47','',450,'http://www.dreamerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/图片38.jpg',